  "description": "<p>Map of Charleston, South Carolina. Made using the Map Patcher by Kronifer and US Demand Generator by slurry.</p>\n<p>Additional demand data as follows:</p>\n<h3>Airports</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Charleston International Airport (ANC)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Universities</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><p>College of Charleston</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Medical University of South Carolina</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Charleston Southern University</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Trident Technical College</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>The Citadel</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Entertainment/Tourism</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><p>Patriots Point Naval Museum</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>South Carolina Aquarium</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Fort Sumter Visitors Center (includes ferry demand)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Fort Moultrie</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Amtrak Station</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Shopping</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><p>Tanger Outlets</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Northwoods Mall</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Citadel Mall</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Military Bases</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><p>Joint Base Charleston (split into 2 demand points)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Naval Weapons Station (split into 3 demand points)</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Coast Guard Station</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
